page.title: 06MY FAMILY IN 1985
page.content: There are four people in my family , my mum , dad, sister and me. I'm 11 years old my sister is 2 years old.I am a boy.I go to Berrynarbor school.I like fishing. I live in Berrynarbor at Lee Side. My grand parents and great grand parents live opposite us. We have one pet, a dog. Also my great grandad has some chickens. We have 2 acres of land,\ acre is used for growing vegetables and the rest is a paddock. At weekends we usually go to Barnstaple,it takes 20 minutes by car. If we don't go to town at weekends I usually play with my friends.Mum usually watches my sister while Dad does some gardening. My nan has 3 greenhouses and sometimes I help her. On sundays I go to church for an hour then I come back and play with my bow and arrows.
